<h2>System Requirements</h2>

<p>There are certain requirements for this system; please ensure that they are all met.  When cleared, the installation will continue upon refreshing the page.</p>

<ul>
	<li>PHP 5.3 or greater</li>
	<li>Apache 2.x with either mod_php or php_cgi support</li>
	<li>Mod Rewrite (not yet supported on non-Apache installations)</li>
	<li>configuration.xml can NOT be written to by apache</li>
	<li>configuration.xml is NOT accessable from the outside world</li>
</ul>
